May Department Stores Co said it namedRonald Tanler as chairman of the company's L.S. Ayresdepartment store division based in Indianapolis, filling along-time vacancy.    It said Robert Friedman continues as president and chiefexecutive officer of L.S. Ayres.    Tanler had served the company as senior vice president andchief financial officer of its St. Louis-based Famous-Barrdepartment store division. Reuter&#3;